    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Choose a class: <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:bard=1\">bard</a>, <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:cleric=1\">cleric</a>, <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:druid=1\">druid</a>, <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:sorcerer=1\">sorcerer</a>, <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:warlock=1\">warlock</a>, or <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:wizard=1\">wizard</a>. You learn two cantrips of your choice from that class's spell list.</p><p>In addition, choose one 1st-level spell to learn from that same list. Using this feat, you can cast the spell once at its lowest level, and you must finish a long rest before you can cast it in this way again.</p><p>Your spellcasting ability for these spells depends on the class you chose: Charisma for <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:bard=1\">bard</a>, <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:sorcerer=1\">sorcerer</a>, or <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:warlock=1\">warlock</a>; Wisdom for <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:cleric=1\">cleric</a> or <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:druid=1\">druid</a>; or Intelligence for <a href=\"https://2014.5e.tools/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:0=1~1=1,flstclass:wizard=1\">wizard</a>.</p></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
